  "title": "Falling Leaves Plus",
  "description": "Beautiful tree-specific falling leaves with branches, acorns, cones, and more.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Twitter&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=x&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"116\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@heyitsfuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Falling Leaves Plus</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> enhances Minecraft's falling leaf particles with detailed, tree-specific visuals that make forests feel more alive and distinctive. Instead of every tree shedding the same simple particle, each leaf type can produce its own unique collection of leaves, branches, acorns, cones, and other natural debris. 🍃</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The mod brings personality to every forest biome. Oak trees release acorns, spruce trees can drop cones, and many leaf types feature multiple particle variations for a richer and more natural appearance. Snow-covered leaves release snowflakes, adding extra atmosphere to winter landscapes. ❄️</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Beyond the built-in effects, this mod is fully resource pack driven. Custom particle textures and behaviors can be added for modded trees and resource packs, making it easy to extend the system far beyond vanilla Minecraft. 🎨</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🍃 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Ambient Falling Leaves:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Expands Minecraft's ambient falling leaves with richer visuals and greater variety.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌳 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Tree-Specific Particles:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Different tree types can produce their own unique leaves, branches, acorns, cones, and other debris.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">✨ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Particle Variations:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Individual leaf types can use multiple particle textures for a more natural and less repetitive look.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">❄️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Snowflake Support:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Snow-covered leaves can spawn snowflakes instead of leaves for a more atmospheric winter experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌧️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Weather-Reactive Effects:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Rain and thunderstorms can increase particle activity and wind strength for livelier storms.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">💨 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Custom Wind and Motion:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Leaves can swirl, drift away, fall at different speeds, and respond to configurable wind direction.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🧱 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Natural Collisions:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Particles can collide with visual block shapes, helping leaves settle more believably on detailed blocks.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⚙️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Flexible Customisation:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Adjust particle density, size, lifetime, wind, gravity, collisions, affected blocks, and more.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">📦 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Resource Pack Driven:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Particle textures and behavior can additionally be customized through resource packs.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/media/1.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INSTALLATION REQUIRED ON CLIENT</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/puzzles-lib\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PUZZLES LIB</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC &amp; NEOFORGE)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FABRIC API</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FORGE CONFIG API PORT</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/configuration.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If available for a mod, configuration is possible directly from in-game using the mod menu (requires </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod Menu</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> by </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Prospector\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Prospector</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> to be installed on Fabric).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For manual configuration using an external text editor all files are found at </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.minecraft/config</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, named as </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-client.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-common.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, or </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-server.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, depending on the type of config. Not all types might exist for a mod, if any at all.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Global particle behavior is configured through the mod config, while individual vanilla and modded leaf types can be customized through resource packs.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Detailed documentation, configuration examples, and a complete reference of all available options can be found in the </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">README.md</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> on GitHub.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/credits.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Special thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/pringlebeaver\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PringleBeaver</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for creating the beautiful falling leaf particle textures that define the look of this mod.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/universal-bone-meal\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/universalbonemeal/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/easy-magic\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easymagic/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/universal-enchants\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/universalenchants/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/studio.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/fallingleavesplus/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n",
